## ৩. 🏗️ Code Quality & Architecture (কোড কোয়ালিটি)

### ✅ Strengths (যা অত্যন্ত ভালো করা হয়েছে)

| বিষয় | বিবরণ | গ্রেড |
|:---|:---|:---:|
| **TypeScript** | সমগ্র codebase TypeScript — well-typed interfaces, enums, clean type exports | **A** |
| **State Management** | `useReducer` + Context — predictable, idempotent actions, clean reducer | **A-** |
| **Data Migration** | `migrateAppState()` — backward compatibility, `dailyProgress → stepProgress` migration | **A** |
| **Test Coverage** | Property-based tests (fast-check) + unit tests — 6 property test suites, 2 unit test files | **B+** |
| **Content Separation** | ৫টি JSON data file (238KB+ content) — code-free content updates | **A** |
| **Error Handling** | ErrorBoundary, save failure alerts, notification graceful degradation | **B+** |
| **Notification Architecture** | Mock fallback for Expo Go, LogBox suppression, identifier-based cancel | **A** |
| **Lifecycle Management** | Background save, foreground refresh, old data cleanup | **A** |
| **Theme Infrastructure** | Light/dark themes, system preference, AsyncStorage persistence | **A-** |
| **Custom Hooks** | `useProgressStats`, `useMilestones`, `useWeeklySummary` — clean separation | **A** |
| **Data Export/Import** | JSON backup with validation, date display, confirmation dialog | **A-** |
| **Haptic Feedback** | Step complete ও checklist toggle-এ vibration | **B+** |
| **Accessibility Effort** | `AccessibilityInfo.isReduceMotionEnabled()` check, some labels | **B** |
| **Onboarding Flow** | 3-step flow (welcome → profile → quit-date), step persistence | **A-** |

---

### 🔶 Remaining Architecture Issues

---

#### ARCH-1: Theme System Adoption Gap (সবচেয়ে জরুরি)

```
theme.tsx (ThemeProvider, useTheme) ✅ তৈরি হয়েছে
├── ব্যবহৃত: Card.tsx, ScreenHeader.tsx, SkeletonScreen.tsx, settings.tsx
└── ব্যবহৃত নয়: 
    ├── index.tsx (Home)         → hardcoded #2E7D32, #f5f5f5
    ├── progress.tsx             → hardcoded #2E7D32, #f5f5f5
    ├── tracker.tsx              → hardcoded
    ├── dua.tsx                  → hardcoded
    ├── library.tsx              → hardcoded
    ├── craving/index.tsx        → hardcoded
    ├── slip-up/index.tsx        → hardcoded
    ├── trigger-log/index.tsx    → hardcoded
    ├── tracker/[step].tsx       → hardcoded
    ├── _layout.tsx              → headerStyle: '#2E7D32' hardcoded
    ├── (tabs)/_layout.tsx       → tabBar colors hardcoded
    ├── ErrorBoundary.tsx        → hardcoded
    ├── ArabicText.tsx           → color '#1a1a1a' hardcoded
    ├── CravingTimer.tsx         → hardcoded
    └── IslamicCard.tsx          → hardcoded
```

> **প্রভাব**: Dark Mode সক্রিয় করলে বেশিরভাগ screen এখনও সাদা ব্যাকগ্রাউন্ডে দেখাবে  
> **সমাধান**: প্রতিটি screen-এ `const { theme } = useTheme();` import করে সব hardcoded color `theme.colors.primary`, `theme.colors.background` ইত্যাদি দিয়ে replace করুন

